  "title": "Part Time Live Stream Host",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>JOVET by JOOP, a Singapore homegrown brand is now expanding into TIKTOK and Shopee live selling.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join JOVET’s TikTok & Shopee live-selling team as a Part-Time Live Host to style outfits, engage viewers, and drive sales through interactive livestream sessions.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Host engaging and interactive live sessions on TikTok, Instagram, and Shopee to promote JOVET products</li><li>Style and try on JOVET outfits during livestreams to showcase product features and inspire viewers</li><li>Communicate clearly with viewers by answering questions and sharing styling tips to enhance customer experience</li><li>Use natural sales skills to encourage viewer purchases and meet sales targets during live sessions</li><li>Commit to hosting afternoon or evening sessions lasting about 2 hours each to maintain consistent live presence</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in live hosting to effectively manage livestream interactions and sales</li><li>Confident, bubbly, and camera-friendly personality to connect with online audiences</li><li>Good communication skills to clearly convey product information and engage viewers</li><li>Natural sales flair to drive conversions during live sessions</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Hourly rates from $20/hour and above</li><li>Flexible working hours</li><li>Additional sales incentives for achieving sales targets</li><li>Interested candidates can send their resume to apply now</li></ul>",
